    <PrimAttribute name="enforcementLevel" id="e007dd03-375f-4e29-af81-81cd43b4a542">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>The enforcementLevel is an int that describes the level of
detail that a move must comply to before this queue will be 
picked.
Level 0 = minimal enforcement, moveFrom MUST apply, moveTo ignored.
Level 1 = Both move to and move from must apply</text>
